Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Timing & Subtitles brought to you by\Nthe Gone with the Shirt team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Don't be upset when the\Nmoon is covered by clouds ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ That's only the wind\Nshowing its love ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ If the stars belong\Nto the sea of sky ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ The moon is what\Nthe tide hopes for ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ When the clouds disappear ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ The moon lights\Nup this world ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ The world becomes\Nstill at this moment ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:01:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Let go of everything ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Those who long for\Nthe color of freedom ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Love carelessly,\Nthen abandon love ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Maybe a vow can\Nlast like the sea ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ As long as the heart\Ndoesn't change ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ That's the last thing I\Nwill worship in my life ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who is playing a\Nsong about love ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Who wouldn't want to\Nhave it completely ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Burn the dust of darkness ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ When the wind blows\Naway the clouds ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ He will return\Nwith the melody ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Mix-Blooded Fox: YingNing{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that if we\Ngive her some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,she will definitely accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there is\None more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How come your power\Nis so strong today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. When I saw Da\NHuang being beaten so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anger rose up in me, and in a second,\NI was unable to control my self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a force of power that\Nseems to be hidden inside my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I become\Nangry, it explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If this force is controlled\Nby your emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then if one day, your\Nemotions go out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this force will also\Nbe out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If this force harms\Nother people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine\Nthe consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I can't even\Nfeel its existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is no way\Nthat I can control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you just have\Nto control your emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then this force won't break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the fact that it\Nwasn't a knife in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a knife in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just...Ka! Ka! Ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's fortunate that what you\Nwere holding in your hand was not a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning went mad, and\Nshowed astonishing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for Zi Fu\Nassisting you on time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't imagine the consequences.\N-Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you were\Nholding was a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm afraid you would\Nbe the one who got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Taoist Cao has lost\Nall of his powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and other Taoists are\Nnot strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this Ying Ning demon\Nto show up in front of Zi Fu again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear aunt, if you don't hold your temper\Nin check, you won't be able to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not smart for us to\Nmove before thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning is a demon after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we possibly\Nwin against her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that I\Nshould tolerate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to, even if\Nyou don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning and Zi Fu are\Ninseparable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to chase\NYing Ning away or kill her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then Zi Fu will hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I think you shouldn't\Npick on Ying Ning too much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ying Ning can't change her demonic\Nnature, can't eliminate her inner evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu will find out himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He can then chase\Nher out by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This way you kill two\Nbirds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your relationship with\NZi Fu won't be hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can also get rid\Nof a thorn in your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Dong Lai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense. What\Nyou're saying makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, little demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tolerate you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just wait, I\Nwill not lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt, slowly, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, it's totally clean in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nworry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she just sweeps\Nthis with her fox tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very clean indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving fox fur everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,lest nobody knows that there is\Nan immortal fox in our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think if you climb this high\NI won't able to talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, the last time I used my fox\Ntail to clean and you didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time, I came here\Nsecretly to clean again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, I didn't\Nuse my fox tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So Ying Ning is the one who\Nmade this place spotless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nworry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know how\Nto pick a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is away\Nfrom wind and sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cleaning for\Ntwenty-four hours a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you clean like this, what\Nwould happen to my garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the flower garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost dawn. You\Ndon't need to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make flower\Npowders of top-quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that mother in-law can accept\Nme as a member of the Wang family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like these powders\Nstill lack something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, did you make\Nall these face powders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These face powders are\Nsweet and very fragrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the best face powders\Nthat I have ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lying to me because\Nyou want me to rest early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. I'm saying the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee you, if someone smell\Nthis, they will definitely like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it... Make\Neveryone like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it lacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A scent that everyone likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be patient everyone. There\Nare too many people inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please line up outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The stock is coming.\NPlease be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will all get to\Nbuy the new powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, you're just on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The stocks inside are\Nalmost sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry and take the goods down.\N-Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, what did you use to\Nmake these fragrant powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How come it's so popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just in our town, people in adjacent towns\Nare also riding their carriages to buy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, today is temple day.\NOur business is really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the young master of\Nthis Fragrant Scent Mill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! I'm\Nso grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She...has been married to her\Nhusband for 20 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He has always been cold to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since she started using\Nour shop's scent powder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,her husband's attitude towards her became so\Nwarm, just like when they were newlyweds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So she was really\Ngrateful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, there are some\Nreceipts on the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and sign them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, there are too\Nmany people inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so just wait for me outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm done, I'll take you\Nto the Temple Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming! I'm coming! I'm coming!\NPlease come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here. Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma! This pearl hairpin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like we are strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...think of it as a\Nnewlywed gift to you and Zi Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, look! This is the hairpin\Nthat Mister Ma just gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma, don't you need to\Nwatch over your shop today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many people at\Nthe Temple Festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your good luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all the business is going\Nto your shop already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have something to do at\Nhome so I'll go do them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ying Ning, let's go. - We are\Nnot going to the Temple Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be going for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up at the Fragrance\NPowder Mill. Let's go back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about it\Nwhen we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, why are we returning to the\NFragrance Powder Mill so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you talking\Nto him earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Mister Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he give you\Na pearl hairpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was waiting for you earlier,\NMister Ma coincidentally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This hair pin is his\Nwedding gift for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop first from changing the topic\Nand asking some nonsense questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me first why we initially agreed\Nto stroll the Temple Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but you suddenly\Nchanged the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the mill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing going\Nwrong in the mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My mood just\Nsuddenly turned bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to go to the\NTemple Festival anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your purpose\Nfor lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're so\Nstupid, so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're easily fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If they won't fool a stupid person\Nlike you, who will they fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You...you even called me stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a stupid person\Nwill wear that hair pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so ugly. Take it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You even called me ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying you're ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that the\Nhair pin is ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not taking it down. I'm\Nfirmly not taking it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You...you just can't\Nbear to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take it down,\Ndon't talk to me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here, Wang Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to go!\NCome back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? My fault? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Little vixen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know the\Nleast bit of etiquette!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're someone else's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing in the middle of the road\Nand talking happily to another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just with this, Zi Fu can\Ndivorce you reasonably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But me and Sir Ma really\Njust chatted a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We also didn't do anything\Nthat's out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still considered my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you considered\NZi Fu's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with Zi Fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you pretending or\Nare you really stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu loves you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cherishes you, sees\Nyou as the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he wouldn't like to see you\Nchatting happily with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He will get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't that be sour?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That flavor in his heart is\Ndefinitely going up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to say it\Nbut can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to say it, but you\Nfeel worse by keeping it inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take good care of\NZi Fu's feelings in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,don't blame me if get\Nimpolite with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, wash your face first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was soaked in the flower\Nbath I especially made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. You don't want\Nto mind me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to choke\Nyourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know that I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't talk to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die from choking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that your anger\Ndidn't come out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry because you\Nlove me, cherish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't like it\Nwhen I talked with Mister Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you, in the future, I won't\Ntalk with Mister Ma or any other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see them, I\Nwill run away fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma Sheng is a person\Nwith evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried that if you get close\Nto him, you might get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got angry today and\Nlost my temper at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being\Nmad at you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu was just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very open-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not jealous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're blushing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it... That\Nyou're jealous, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll look for Sir Zhu, Sir\NNiou, and Sir Ma tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to bite me?\NI won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie, the new batch of fragrance powder\Nthat Ying Ning made was really very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon opening the store today, the fragrance\Npowders were immediately sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, our business\Nis really booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our stocks cannot meet\Nthe demand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's needed,\Nhire more workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a chance that\Nwe shouldn't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Da Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ying Ning - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Why are you so careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. - Were you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...only know to run, to\Ncause trouble, to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not knowing a bit of\Nrules and regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you some high\Nquality textile fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wear them, you'll\Nlook more dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still our\NWang family's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop losing our face within\Nand outside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you now. I'll make sure\Nnot to lose face...not lose face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, I\Nonly have one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need this\Nmuch textile fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I only have one head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I wear so many\Nhead pieces and jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have\Nso much nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already bought them\Nfor you so just use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already. Stop\Nfighting already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting already!\NHurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't cause trouble here.\N- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Dong Lai. Why\Nare they fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This man and a brothel\Ngirl are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife will not allow him to marry a\Nconcubine so their fight extended up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That main wife said that because that brothel\Ngirl used our shop's fragrance powder;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hence, his husband\Ngot bewitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting! What are you doing?\NGo already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop fighting already.\N- Stop it. Don't fight already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry and go -\NStop fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why are you hitting people?\N- Stop fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- All of you stop it.\N- Stop fighting already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry and go.\N- Stop fighting already. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken care\Nof the shop front.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems everything's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This...what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How come they started\Nfighting just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked around a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, within the whole,\Nthere are a lot of wives
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who bought our shop's\Nfragrance scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They suddenly attract\Nthe opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the brother girls, their\Nbusinesses were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Attracting a lot of regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men were attracted\Nto them up to a point
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are willing to leave\Ntheir wives and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So rumors started spreading that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,our fragrance powder is\Nmixed with seducing drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of wives have started\Nnot to buy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You...explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were concocting these fragrance\Npowders, what ingredients did you put in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...just added some\Nmagic called charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You did an evil spell on\Nthe the fragrance powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Charm can make people happy\Nand attract people easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some evil spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, aren't a lot\Nof wives who used it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,having improvement in their relationship\Nwith their husbands, becoming sweeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...the Charm Power will not\Ncause people to become aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know why such\Na thing has happened today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not allowed to touch my\Nfragrance powder from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not make\Nfragrance powder here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, charm is\Nreally nothing bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a magic that\Nwill make people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When people are happy,\Ntheir face will glow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will attract\Nother people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to use this magic\Nto make lovers become family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and make husbands and wives live in\Nharmony, so that everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what happened today\Nis not what I intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But most relationships\Nin this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,don't need an outer\Nforce to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it‘s all about destiny.\NWe'll just have to let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will destiny help everyone\Nto find their love?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, if it is yours,\Nthen you will have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is not yours, then you\Nshouldn't force it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you are in\Nthe human world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you shouldn't\Nuse your magic anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I just wanted\Nto help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a good thing\Nthat you wanted to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but think about it\Nclosely, sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't even control\Nyour own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the powder with charm\Ncame out wrong because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, we don't want anyone\Nelse to get hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you promise me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you won't use\Nmagic anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm saving people,\NI can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, except when\Nyou're saving others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let's make\Na pinky promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect someone wise and\Nintelligent like Madam Wang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to be deceived by a\Nlittle fox spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Wang, you don't really\Nbelieve that this fox spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is making flower powders for the\Nbenefit of your mill, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My powder actually...sold well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only a minor flaw\Nin between the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Wang, in my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,this powder made by Ying\NNing is very attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It even greatly improved\Nyour attitude toward her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing that for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She is trying to curry\Nfavor with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Wang, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she gets to control you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't everything you have,\Nincluding Mister Wang,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,be taken over by her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu loves her so\Nmuch right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He is totally obsessed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I don't know how\NI can kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, I\Nreally can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so mysteriously,\Nyou must have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Wang, this can be tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,or it can be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to all of\Nthis is Mister Wang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can think of a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Mister Wang abandon\Nthis little fox spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,take away her protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then dealing with her\Nwill be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma, here,\Nhave another drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, more wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma, have some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma, here. Make\Nyourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you standing\Nhere, Zi Fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here! Sit down, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma heard that our\Nmill had some trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,since our families have been\Nfriends for all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he came here to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us? What help?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma lent us some money
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we could continue\Nto operate the mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a philanthropist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm helping, I\Nstill need basic revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family can lend\Nyou the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but...you have to use\Nthe mill as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you gain a profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the ownership of your house and\Nland will be returned to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but we\Ndon't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a chance you\Ncould find anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma came here in person,\Njust to talk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, our family is\Nnot at a dead end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one incident, we\Ncould think of another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When the powder\Nmill is in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone in the Wang's family\Nis worried about it. -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't\Nconsider for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you should consider for the\Nwomen in your house. -Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when you have\Nsuch a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to let her bear\Nhardships with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning is my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let her go\Nthrough hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our family's affair, you\Nhave no right to get involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to lend you the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a guy who cares for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let such things\Nhappen to Miss Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get more wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ying Ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.30,0:24:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already talked\Nwith Madam Wang.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to throw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.04,0:24:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, how could you say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.45,0:24:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you borrow from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His intention is not pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If he offers to\Nhelp us right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he must be after something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.94,0:24:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, how can I just leave the mill\Nthe way it is and not do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must follow what\NI say this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already talked this\Nover with Mister Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.10,0:24:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll write a note tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.39,0:24:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to\Nreject him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.04,0:24:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will reject him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:25:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so beautiful\Nunder the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.69,0:25:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ma, you're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.76,0:25:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.30,0:25:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop hitting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.10,0:25:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hitting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop hitting him! -Son!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.70,0:25:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-ZiFu! -Son, stop hitting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.80,0:25:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, Wang Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.00,0:25:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I lend money to you\Nout of kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you pay me with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.30,0:25:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! That is very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.60,0:25:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't lend you any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.20,0:25:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die from\Nhunger and poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.91,0:25:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not take a\Npenny from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.40,0:25:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Zi Fu! -Zi Fu, Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.31,0:25:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.00,0:25:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever borrow from Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have me in this family!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.40,0:25:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, where is Zi Fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:25:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He went out early\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.77,0:26:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he is going\Nto find some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since our mill got into\Ntrouble, rumors have spread...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.50,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and now, nobody dares to buy the\Npowders made by our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.03,0:26:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our business is getting\Nworse everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.40,0:26:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we will have close the\Nshop...sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.40,0:26:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that with\NZi Fu's skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll definitely be able\Nto take care of it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.30,0:26:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, no need\Nto worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In this town, other\Nthan the Ma Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.80,0:26:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody else is\Nwilling to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.15,0:26:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this all because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.98,0:26:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to put some evil\Nspell on those fragrance powders?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.14,0:26:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Causing so much trouble now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.82,0:26:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the use of apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.65,0:26:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ma was initially\Nour mill's only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.96,0:27:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And again because of a bad\Nluck person like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.09,0:27:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he was beaten badly by Zi Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.21,0:27:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting our only chance\Nto live get beaten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.94,0:27:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can we do? Is\Nthere any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.88,0:27:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.08,0:27:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe there's a chance\Nto turn this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.10,0:27:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we make up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.74,0:27:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ma is not really\Nsomeone who is unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.57,0:27:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, he was just drunk;\Nhence, he disrespected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.00,0:27:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You...go look for him and\Napologize sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.60,0:27:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us should\Ntake a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.10,0:27:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him stairs to go down to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.30,0:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe, he will\Nchange his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When he changes his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.55,0:27:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's a chance that he'll\Nbe willing to lend us money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This...I am afraid I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.60,0:27:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I already promised Zi Fu\Nnot to see Master Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.08,0:27:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go behind Zi Fu's back\Nand apologize to Master Ma,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.73,0:27:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu will get angry\Nif he learns about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.62,0:28:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.36,0:28:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to see the\Nfragrance mill be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.37,0:28:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to see Zi Fu\Ngoing out everyday bowing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.80,0:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and begging people to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.70,0:28:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.26,0:28:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't that reason enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.04,0:28:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you can help turn\Nthings around with the mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.63,0:28:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,will Zi Fu even blame\Nyou afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.37,0:28:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I blame you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.90,0:28:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ma, you're\Na forgiving man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.70,0:28:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll represent Zi Fu\Nand apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.10,0:28:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please drink this cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Miss Ying Ning\Nhas already spoken,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.67,0:28:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be bad for\Nme to refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.28,0:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then with this cup of wine, I'll treat\Neverything as if it were in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Master Ma is\Nreally a generous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.51,0:28:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come...drink it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.40,0:29:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These wines are really good.\NThe dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are not enough. I'll\Ngo order some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.76,0:29:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, please sit down.\NI'll go order instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. How can we let Master\NMa drink here by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.00,0:29:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Accompany Master Ma\Nin drinking wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.90,0:29:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.00,0:29:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.16,0:29:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This wine is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot not drink it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.70,0:29:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or do you not want to help the\NWang's Fragrance Mill anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.00,0:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ma, we really\Nneed this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.00,0:29:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you to help\Nus just this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.10,0:29:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To help you is okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will depend\Non your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.94,0:29:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.42,0:29:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you want me to perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.24,0:29:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to tell jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.56,0:30:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You put a drug in the wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.06,0:30:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it's yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.90,0:30:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...the one who put\Nthe drug was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.30,0:30:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Madam Wang.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.88,0:30:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.19,0:30:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Wang and me have already agreed on\Nconditions for me to help their fragrance mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.30,0:30:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you... are one\Nof those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.30,0:30:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, you\Nreally smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie, look. Smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.80,0:31:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers really\Nbloomed well this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.40,0:31:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me. Why did you\Nsell me to Ma Sheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.71,0:31:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fragrance mill was initially doing\Nwell and suddenly met so many problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.25,0:31:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it all your doing? If you don't\Ntake responsibility, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think even if I have you\Nkilled, it won't be excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.64,0:31:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, what\Nis going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.06,0:31:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom earlier took me to\Nsee Master Ma to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.04,0:31:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She secretly drugged me and let\NMaster Ma sexually harass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.97,0:31:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Made me one of the conditions for him to\Nhelp the fragrance mill and sold me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.43,0:31:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This... Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, do you really\Nbeliever her lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.65,0:31:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Making up stories\Nin broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.11,0:31:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaming it all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.29,0:31:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This clearly is to incite\Ndisharmony between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.30,0:31:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.30,0:32:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, I am your\Nbiological mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.80,0:32:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you believe me or\Nnot, you weigh it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.60,0:32:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I never went out this whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.10,0:32:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I take\NYing Ning to a bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.20,0:32:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe\Nme, then it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.90,0:32:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.58,0:32:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...yes... Auntie was at home all day\Ntending to the flowers and cutting grasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.05,0:32:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't go out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.30,0:32:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, they are lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.30,0:32:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.30,0:32:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,doing adulterous acts and\Nusing this to cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.90,0:32:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Insane girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.80,0:32:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.60,0:32:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning! This thing...I will\Ndefinitely investigate it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.40,0:32:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, you must believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.90,0:32:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the ones who are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.58,0:33:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't. Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.72,0:33:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me. You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.52,0:33:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.55,0:33:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.01,0:33:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.73,0:33:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.73,0:33:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- I told you to stop!\N- I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.61,0:33:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.04,0:33:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.19,0:33:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants me to die... She...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.00,0:33:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.10,0:33:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come, Mom, get up.\N- She wants me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.92,0:33:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help me to stand.\N- Mom, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.70,0:34:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu! Zi Fu, I didn't! Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.06,0:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I already did what\Nyou asked of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.00,0:34:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused that Madam Wang\Nto fall and get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.20,0:34:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Zi Fu also thought that\Nit's the doing of that vixen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.32,0:34:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can now follow our\Nagreement and let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.40,0:34:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.89,0:34:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But...since you're task is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.53,0:34:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no use keeping\Nyou alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.00,0:34:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Fei, you went\Nagainst your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.20,0:34:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Despicable! Cao Fei!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.13,0:35:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You went against your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.68,0:35:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Timing & Subtitles brought to you by\Nthe Gone with the Shirt team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.85,0:35:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.40,0:35:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just knew that\Nyou would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.60,0:35:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You must believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mother-in-law...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.40,0:35:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.10,0:35:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,From the time Ma Sheng went\Nto the fragrance mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.10,0:35:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew that it was a\Nscheme that Mom had set-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.10,0:35:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you for\Nsuggesting this plan to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.30,0:35:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to let Ma Sheng anger\Nthat evil little fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.93,0:36:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her hurt me in\Nfront of Zi Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.33,0:36:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, I can force Zi Fu
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.93,0:36:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose between her and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu is a filial child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.10,0:36:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He will definitely leave\Nthat evil little fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mother-in-law just\Nwants me to get angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.10,0:36:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she conspired\Nwith Ma Sheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.50,0:36:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you used the tree to injure\Nmy mom in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.64,0:36:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing...is also\Nhard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.60,0:36:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, I was\Nindeed very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.70,0:36:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remembered our agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.50,0:36:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I tried very hard to\Nsuppress that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I really wanted\Nto kill your mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.50,0:36:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she should have died a thousand\Ntimes, ten thousand times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.77,0:36:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can also leave no\Nevidence, attack invisibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.00,0:36:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I attack in\Nfront of everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.64,0:36:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said...is\Nindeed reasonable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.22,0:36:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But why could that tree move?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.77,0:36:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that is a demon tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.89,0:36:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.17,0:36:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Madam Wang, you still\Nwere wrong with one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.31,0:37:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who cast a spell to\Nharm you wasn't Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.97,0:37:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's me who forced your flower\Ngarden's Demon Tree to injure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.00,0:37:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must you hurt me? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just my backup plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.70,0:37:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that Ying Ning was able to\Ncontrol herself and not attack you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then wouldn't our plan\Njust go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.14,0:37:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then your injuries? - My injuries\Nhave already healed long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.02,0:37:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And my power has returned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.39,0:37:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.98,0:37:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that little vixen dares\Nto enter our house again,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you should use magic\Nto make her disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.10,0:37:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.00,0:37:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I already went\Nto see Ma Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.64,0:38:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.30,0:38:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What Ying Ning said was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.20,0:38:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You used Ma Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? She then can use\Nevil magic to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.40,0:38:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to end my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not me. It's the\Ndoings of a demon tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.00,0:38:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, didn't you meticulously\Nset-up all these
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.70,0:38:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just to make me drive\NYing Ning out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.00,0:38:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Ying Ning will do as you\Nwish and leave the Wang family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.97,0:38:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will also leave\Nwith Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.11,0:38:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You...what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.08,0:38:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... I love Ying Ning deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.70,0:38:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to spend my\Nlifetime with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.40,0:38:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also want to be filial\Nto you and serve you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.21,0:38:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But how is it that two very usual\Nthings cannot exist together?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.14,0:38:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have a way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.13,0:38:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only carry the infamy\Nof being an unfilial son
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.76,0:38:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave with Ying Ning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...just\Nleave your Mom and go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.72,0:38:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I will wait for you\Nto open your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.86,0:39:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The day you accept Ying Ning\Nwill be the day I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.12,0:39:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, thank you for\Nbringing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.97,0:39:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ying Ning, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.25,0:39:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.75,0:39:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zi Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.74,0:39:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I really underestimated the\Nrelationship between these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.82,0:39:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that\Nit was this stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.41,0:39:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a scheme to distance them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.06,0:39:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has been seen through by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.84,0:39:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taoist Cao, go and\Nkill that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ying Ning's demonic\Npower is too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.06,0:39:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want to destroy her,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.70,0:39:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid that we cannot estimate\Nthe consequence we have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.20,0:39:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think about it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.90,0:39:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what\Nconsequence I must pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.60,0:39:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to kill Ying Ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.10,0:40:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever you're overtaken by the\NFire of Rage, your power will erupt,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.80,0:40:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and life will be destroyed\Nwherever you go.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.89,0:40:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the Fire of Rage that makes\Nyou lose your original character.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.92,0:40:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave here and go back\Nto Green Hill with me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.44,0:40:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! If I don't kill Cao Fei, I\Nwill never go back to Green Hill.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.48,0:40:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can finally see you\Nget angry again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.70,0:40:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come! Come and kill me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.62,0:40:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cao Fei...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.90,0:40:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though I cannot kill you,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.30,0:40:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will use the rest of\Nmy life to curse you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.40,0:40:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, you will surely die.{\i}
